\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{FIN}_{\leqslant}^{\left[a,b\right]}\left(\sigma\right)\subseteq\mathbf{FIN}^{\left[a,b\right]}\left(\sigma\cup\left\{ \leqslant\right\} \right)$
\end_inset

