\begin_inset Formula $\sigma\cup\left\{ \leqslant\right\} $
\end_inset

-Strukturen über 
\begin_inset Formula $\left[a,b\right]$
\end_inset

, wobei 
\begin_inset Formula $\leqslant$
\end_inset

